      "para_id": "Q004125.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Amar-Suena , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Baddari , overseer of the dumudaba workers , child of Gulum , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
